data.description: Waterfront home on Poquito Bayou with a pool WITHOUT any worries of waterfront living or a big waterfront price!! Live out your Florida dreams in this beautiful home featuring a private pool on a secluded neighborhood street with 22' on a protected deep-water bayou! Just a few steps from the garage, down a private road, you will find your waterfront paradise with a NEW dock on picturesque Poquito Bayou!! A HUGE front porch with multiple French doors welcomes you into this lovely 1-story home with a split floorplan and multiple living areas. When you enter through the wide foyer, you will find the formal dining room on the left that is open to the living room. The tiled living room leads to the kitchen that is open to the family room accented by lovely wood floors and a cheery fireplace. This large kitchen features cherry cabinets, granite counter tops, a center island, a convenient breakfast bar as well as a double oven and gas stove. The split bedroom floor plan provides privacy for the master suite with its two walk-in closets and private bath. A fourth bedroom across from the dining room can also serve as an office and the convenient full bath in the hall has outside access for easy use from your salt-chlorinated pool and hot tub. Bedrooms 2 and 3 on the left side of the house share a jack-n-jill bath with a dual sink vanity. The spacious laundry room and oversized 2-car garage with workshop space round out this incredible home. The oversized covered porch along the back of the home overlooks the gunite pool with a spill over hot tub. There is a large paver patio surrounding the pool as well as a spacious fenced yard with a yard building. Additional noteworthy features include NEW paint, 2020 roof, 2017 HVAC system, tankless water heater, NO carpet, raised ceilings and crown molding. There is also a natural gas generator for the whole house. Bring your boat and pool toys and enjoy living the good life!!
